completing this form, the completer of this form must, prior to its inclusion, inform them of the terms set forth in the preceding paragraphs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="estatic-txt1">\r\n	<strong>GOTEO</strong> has adopted the necessary measures to avoid the alteration, loss, treatment or unauthorized access of personal data, taking into account at all times of the state of the technology, however, the user should be aware that internet security measures are not impregnable.\r\n	<p>\r\n		This page uses Google Analytics, an analytical service for the web by Google, Inc.,a company from Delaware whose main office is in 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View (California), CA 94043, United States (&quot;Google&quot;). Google Analytics uses &quot;cookies&quot;, they are text files placed on your computer, to help the website analyze the use made by users of the web site. The information generated by the cookie about your use of the website (including your IP address) will be transmitted to and stored by Google on servers in the United States. Google will use this information on our behalf in order to keep track of your use of the website, compiling reports of the activity for the website operators and providing other services relating to website activity and Internet usage. Google may also transfer this information to third parties when required by law, or where such third parties process the information on Google''s behalf. Google will not associate your IP address with any other data held by Google. You can refuse treatment of the data or information by rejecting the use of cookies by selecting the appropriate setting of your browser, however, you should know that if you do you might not be able use the full functionality of this website. By using this website you consent to the processing of data about you by Google in the manner and for the purposes described above.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n');
REPLACE INTO `page_node` (`page`, `node`, `lang`, `content`) VALUES('privacy', 'goteo', 'es', '<div class="estatic-txt0">\r\n	En cumplimiento de la Ley Org&aacute;nica 15/1999, de 13 de diciembre, de Protecci&oacute;n de Datos de Car&aacute;cter Personal, le informamos que los datos personales que nos suministre a trav&eacute;s de la activaci&oacute;n de su cuenta en <strong>GOTEO</strong> pasar&aacute;n a formar parte de un fichero titularidad de <strong>FUNDACION FUENTES ABIERTAS</strong>. Sus datos de car&aacute;cter personal ser&aacute;n utilizados para la gesti&oacute;n y administraci&oacute;n de la plataforma consistente en la posibilidad de apoyar y financiar proyectos emprendedores, as&iacute; como para la puesta en contacto entre los miembros de la misma.\r\n	\r\n<p>\r\nAsimismo le informamos que puede ejercitar sus derechos de <a href="http://www.goteo.org/user/login">acceso</a>, <a href="http://www.goteo.org/dashboard/profile">rectificaci&oacute;n</a>, <a href="http://www.goteo.org//user/leave">cancelaci&oacute;n</a> y oposici&oacute;n.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>\r\nEn todo momento el usuario debe ser consciente que est&aacute; accediendo a una plataforma abierta para apoyar proyectos de emprendedores, innovadores sociales y creativos cuyo objetivo es la puesta en com&uacute;n de sus proyectos, necesidades, etc. por ello acepta y consiente que sus datos puedan ser accesibles a otros miembros de la plataforma. El usuario tiene la posibilidad de establecer el grado de privacidad de sus datos.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		En ning&uacute;n caso los responsables de <strong>GOTEO</strong> venden, alquilan ni ponen a disposici&oacute;n de terceras personas los datos personales proporcionados por los Usuarios de la plataforma.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		El Usuario garantiza que los datos personales facilitados son veraces y se hace responsable de informar sobre cualquier modificaci&oacute;n en los mismos. El Usuario ser&aacute; el &uacute;nico responsable de cualquier da&ntilde;o o perjuicio, directo o indirecto, que pudiera ocasionar a los responsables de <strong>GOTEO</strong> o a cualquier tercero a causa de la cumplimentaci&oacute;n de los formularios con datos falsos, inexactos, incompletos o no actualizados. En el caso de que deban incluirse datos de car&aacute;cter personal referentes a personas f&iacute;sicas distintas de la que cumplimenta el presente formulario deber&aacute;, con car&aacute;cter previo a su inclusi&oacute;n, informarles de los extremos contenidos en los p&aacute;rrafos anteriores.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="estatic-txt1">\r\n	<strong>GOTEO</strong> ha adoptado las medidas necesarias para evitar la alteraci&oacute;n, p&eacute;rdida, tratamiento o acceso no autorizado de los datos personales, habida cuenta en todo momento del estado de la tecnolog&iacute;a, no obstante, el usuario debe ser consciente de que las medidas de seguridad en Internet no son inexpugnables.\r\n	<p>\r\n		Esta p&aacute;gina web utiliza Google Analytics, un servicio anal&iacute;tico de web prestado por Google, Inc., una compa&ntilde;&iacute;a de Delaware cuya oficina principal est&aacute; en 1600 Amphitheatre Parkway, Mountain View (California), CA 94043, Estados Unidos (&quot;Google&quot;). Google Analytics utiliza &quot;cookies&quot;, que son archivos de texto ubicados en su ordenador, para ayudar al website a analizar el uso que hacen los usuarios del sitio web. La informaci&oacute;n que genera la cookie acerca de su uso del website (incluyendo su direcci&oacute;n IP) ser&aacute; directamente transmitida y archivada por Google en los servidores de Estados Unidos. Google usar&aacute; esta informaci&oacute;n por cuenta nuestra con el prop&oacute;sito de seguir la pista de su uso del website, recopilando informes de la actividad del website y prestando otros servicios relacionados con la actividad del website y el uso de Internet. Google podr&aacute; transmitir dicha informaci&oacute;n a terceros cuando as&iacute; se lo requiera la legislaci&oacute;n, o cuando dichos terceros procesen la informaci&oacute;n por cuenta de Google. Google no asociar&aacute; su direcci&oacute;n IP con ning&uacute;n otro dato del que disponga Google. Puede Usted rechazar el tratamiento de los datos o la informaci&oacute;n rechazando el uso de cookies mediante la selecci&oacute;n de la configuraci&oacute;n apropiada de su navegador, sin embargo, debe Usted saber que si lo hace puede ser que no pueda usar la plena funcionabilidad de este website. Al utilizar este website Usted consiente el tratamiento de informaci&oacute;n acerca de Usted por Google en la forma y para los fines arriba indicados.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n');
REPLACE INTO `page_node` (`page`, `node`, `lang`, `content`) VALUES('terms', 'goteo', 'nl', '<div class="estatic-txt2">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<strong>OPEN SOURCE SOCIETY	</strong> (Hereafter OSC), promotor of <strong>GOTEO</strong> complies with the requirements established in the law 34/2002, of 11 July, of services of the information society and electronic commerce, and the law 56/2007, of 28 December of measures to promote the information society, as well as the organic law 15/1999, of 13 December, on protection of data of a Personal nature and its implementing regulations (RD 1720/2007, of 21 December, approving the regulation on development and organic law 15/1999 of protection of Personal data) to that end has created the following conditions of use:</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<h3>\r\n		<span class="estatic-blue-green">OPEN SOURCE SOCIETY</span></h3>\r\n	<p>\r\n		The present conditions of use regulate the access and the use of the platform, including the contents and services available to users in and/or through the community, either by the Foundation, either by their users, or by any third party.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Also, within the platform there is a possibility that the user access to the area to create or support projects, shall be subject to particular conditions.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span class="estatic-blue-green"><strong>FIRST: OBJECT OF THE SERVICE</strong></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		GOTEO mainly offers a free service where registered users can access an open platform to propose or support projects of entrepreneurs, creative, and social innovators as well as putting in contact users of the platform.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span class="estatic-blue-green"><strong>SECOND: CONDICIONS</strong></span></p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		The use of GOTEO will be subject to the following conditions, which may be updated periodically, however GOTEO will send notice of the modification of the General conditions or the privacy policy. If the User decides not to accept the Conditions he(she) will have to abstain from gaining access and/or to use of the contents and/or services offered in the platform.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		GOTEO reserves the right to improve, modify or suppress, unilaterally and without prior notice, services and/or contents of the said community according to different criteria.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Obligation to make proper use of the portal: The User undertakes to make proper use of the platform and to not use it for illegal activities or contrary to good faith and the law (merely indicative and not exhaustive); to provoke damages in the physical and logical systems of the person in charge, of its providers or of third persons, to introduce or to spread in the network computer viruses or any other physical or logical systems that are capable of provoking the damages previously mentioned,not to mention all those who violate or contravene the honour, person or family and privacy of persons, of the rights of property and of anything else belonging to a third party as a consequence of the transmission, dissemination, storage, making available, reception, obtaining or access to the contents or the image of third parties;the realization of acts of disloyal competition and illicit publicity as a consequence of the transmission, dissemination, storage, availability, reception, obtaining or access to the contents; the lack of veracity, accuracy, completeness, relevance and/or currency of the contents leaving the user, in any case, GOTEO harmless against any claim, judicial or extrajudicial.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		The User is solely in charge of the contents and files put at his disposal in the portal, for it he promises not to publish (or to upload) any file (video, audio, text, etc.) that is subject to rights of intellectual property (or industrialist) of third parties, unless the legal holder of the above mentioned rights has granted him a license or formal authorization in accordance with the license that applies currently in the portal.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		GOTEO excludes any liability for damages of any nature
